@startuml
title Decision Intelligence API - SLI/SLO/Error Budget Activity

start

:Ingest observability signals;
note right
Prometheus / Blackbox / OpenSearch / Kubernetes
end note

:Evaluate service-level indicators;

:Compute availability, latency and error rate;

:Compare SLI values against SLO policy;

if (SLO breached?) then (yes)
  :Create SLO violation event;

  :Calculate error budget burn;

  if (Error budget exhausted?) then (yes)
    :Classify reliability risk as HIGH;
    :Escalate incident priority;
    :Recommend conservative action;
    :Prevent unsafe automated remediation;
  else (no)
    :Classify reliability risk as MEDIUM;
    :Recommend investigation or controlled action;
  endif

else (no)
  :Classify reliability risk as LOW;
  :Continue normal decision flow;
endif

:Attach SLO context to incident decision;
note right
Decision output includes:
- current SLI value
- SLO target
- budget remaining
- burn rate
- risk level
end note

:Persist result in PostgreSQL;

:Expose metrics and API response;

stop

@enduml





